text: Amy Sedaris (born March 29, 1961) is an American writer, actress and comedian. She played Jerri Blank in Strangers with Candy on Comedy Central. She played Rachel Hoffberg in Maid in Manhattan. She is the voice of Foxy Loxy in Chicken Little and its subsequent television series. She was the voice of Princess Carolyn in BoJack Horseman. Sedaris was born in Endicott, New York.
